Berikut adalah implementasi **Dependency Injection Container** yang aman dan efisien menggunakan PHP. Implementasi ini dirancang untuk lingkungan produksi dengan pertimbangan keamanan (mencegah arbitrary class instantiation) dan performa.

### Kelas Container (`Container.php`)

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace SherifNetwork\Core;

use ReflectionClass;
use ReflectionException;
use Exception;

class Container
{
    protected array $bindings = [];
    protected array $instances = [];
    protected array $singletons = [];

    /**
     * Bind a class or interface to a concrete implementation.
     */
    public function bind(string $abstract, $concrete = null): void
    {
        if ($concrete === null) {
            $concrete = $abstract;
        }

        if (!is_callable($concrete) && !is_string($concrete)) {
            throw new Exception("Concrete must be a string class name or a callable.");
        }

        $this->bindings[$abstract] = $concrete;
    }

    /**
     * Register a singleton binding.
     */
    public function singleton(string $abstract, $concrete = null): void
    {
        $this->singletons[$abstract] = true;
        $this->bind($abstract, $concrete);
    }

    /**
     * Resolve a class from the container.
     * 
     * SECURITY WARNING: Do not pass user input directly into $abstract.
     * This can lead to Remote Code Execution (RCE) if allowed classes are not whitelisted.
     */
    public function make(string $abstract)
    {
        // Check for existing instance (Singleton)
        if (isset($this->instances[$abstract]) && isset($this->singletons[$abstract])) {
            return $this->instances[$abstract];
        }

        $concrete = $this->bindings[$abstract] ?? $abstract;

        try {
            if (is_callable($concrete)) {
                $object = call_user_func($concrete, $this);
            } else {
                $object = $this->build($concrete);
            }
        } catch (ReflectionException $e) {
            throw new Exception("Target class [{$concrete}] does not exist or cannot be instantiated.", 0, $e);
        }

        // Store singleton instance
        if (isset($this->singletons[$abstract])) {
            $this->instances[$abstract] = $object;
        }

        return $object;
    }

    /**
     * Build a class using Reflection.
     */
    protected function build(string $class): object
    {
        $reflector = new ReflectionClass($class);

        if (!$reflector->isInstantiable()) {
            throw new Exception("Target class [{$class}] is not instantiable.");
        }

        $constructor = $reflector->getConstructor();

        if ($constructor === null) {
            return new $class;
        }

        $dependencies = $constructor->getParameters();
        $resolvedDeps = [];

        foreach ($dependencies as $dependency) {
            $type = $dependency->getType();

            if ($type === null) {
                 // If no type hint, check for default value
                 if ($dependency->isDefaultValueAvailable()) {
                     $resolvedDeps[] = $dependency->getDefaultValue();
                 } else {
                     throw new Exception("Unresolvable dependency in [{$class}]: {$dependency->getName()}");
                 }
                 continue;
            }

            $dependencyClass = $type->getName();

            // Recursive resolution
            $resolvedDeps[] = $this->make($dependencyClass);
        }

        return $reflector->newInstanceArgs($resolvedDeps);
    }
}
```

### Contoh Penggunaan (`index.php`)

```php
<?php

require_once 'vendor/autoload.php';

use SherifNetwork\Core\Container;

// Define Classes
class DatabaseConnection {
    public function connect() { return "Connected to DB"; }
}

class UserRepository {
    protected $db;
    public function __construct(DatabaseConnection $db) {
        $this->db = $db;
    }
    public function find() { return $this->db->connect(); }
}

class UserService {
    protected $repo;
    public function __construct(UserRepository $repo) {
        $this->repo = $repo;
    }
    public function getUser() { return $this->repo->find(); }
}

// Initialize Container
$container = new Container();

// Bindings
$container->singleton(DatabaseConnection::class);
$container->bind(UserRepository::class);
$container->bind(UserService::class);

// Resolve
$service = $container->make(UserService::class);
echo $service->getUser(); // Output: Connected to DB
```

### Catatan Keamanan Kritikal

1.  **Input User**: Jangan pernah meneruskan input pengguna (GET/POST) langsung ke metode `make()`. Ini adalah vektor **Remote Code Execution (RCE)**. Jika pengguna bisa mengontrol nama class, mereka bisa menginstantiasi class berbahaya yang ada di server.
2.  **Whitelisting**: Jika Anda harus membuat factory dinamis, implementasikan whitelist class yang diizinkan sebelum memanggil `new ReflectionClass()`.
3.  **Autoloading**: Pastikan autoloader (Composer) dikonfigurasi dengan benar. Class yang tidak terdaftar tidak akan bisa di-resolve, yang sebenarnya bagus untuk keamanan (fail safe).

